
To run the search script you need to specify the RAMADDA to search.

You can do this in the command line, e.g.:
   search.sh -repos http://ramadda.org/repository -user userid password

Or you can  set environment variables in ramaddaenv.sh or in your shell 
environment that specify the repository and user id


export RAMADDA_CLIENT_REPOSITORY=http://localhost/repository
export RAMADDA_CLIENT_USER=
export RAMADDA_CLIENT_PASSWORD=

